---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Physical AI Workshop">
  <div class="workshop-container">
    <div class="hero-section">
      <img src="/events/2025/physical-ai-workshop-poster.png" alt="Physical AI Workshop Poster" class="poster" />
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>Physical AI Workshop</h1>
        <div class="event-details">
          <p class="date">🗓️ 2025년 8월 14일 (목) 14:00-18:00</p>
          <p class="location">📍 로보티즈 캠퍼스</p>
        </div>
        <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSff0Sh3kSIl31J6mj4DX-Q5n5DCl9LYnqH3ZsTN3K8gydznXA/viewform?usp=sharing&ouid=109247284085622604521" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="register-btn">
          참가 신청하기
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="event-info">
      <h2>행사 소개</h2>
      <p>SUDO REMOVE와 PAIS 컨소시엄이 함께하는 Physical AI Workshop에 여러분을 초대합니다!</p>
      <p>로봇 개발의 문턱을 낮추고, Physical AI의 미래를 함께 만들어갈 개발자와 연구자들을 위한 실습 중심의 워크숍입니다.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="speakers">
      <h2>발표자 소개</h2>
      <div class="speakers-grid">
        <div class="speaker-card">
          <h3>콘북 최사가 준비하는<br/>Physical AI 시대</h3>
          <p class="speaker-name">콘북 최사가</p>
          <p class="speaker-info">🎙️ 브랜드 소개<br/>Physical AI와 로봇 교육 플랫폼의 미래에 대한 비전을 공유합니다.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="speaker-card">
          <h3>VLA, Physical AI를<br/>구현하기 위한 AI</h3>
          <p class="speaker-name">조환규 박사</p>
          <p class="speaker-info">Cognitive Research Engineer<br/>Seoul AI's VisionVerse 연구원</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="speaker-card">
          <h3>로봇 스타트업에서<br/>바라보는 Physical AI</h3>
          <p class="speaker-name">황정섭 대표</p>
          <p class="speaker-info">주식회사 아이디오 대표<br/>도쿄대 박사 출신 로봇 전문가</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="speaker-card">
          <h3>Physical AI 시대를<br/>준비하는 문서 (Q&A)</h3>
          <p class="speaker-name">박성우 연구원</p>
          <p class="speaker-info">MIT 박사과정 중 Physical AI 연구<br/>텔레오퍼레이션 및 데이터셋 구축 전문가</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="hands-on">
      <h2>실습 세션</h2>
      <div class="robot-preview">
        <h3>로보티즈 견학</h3>
        <p>로보티즈 캠퍼스 투어와 함께 최신 로봇 기술을 직접 체험해보세요.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="registration">
      <h2>참가 신청</h2>
      <p>Physical AI의 미래를 함께 만들어갈 분들의 많은 참여 부탁드립니다.</p>
      <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSff0Sh3kSIl31J6mj4DX-Q5n5DCl9LYnqH3ZsTN3K8gydznXA/viewform?usp=sharing&ouid=109247284085622604521" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="register-btn-large">
        참가 신청 바로가기
      </a>
    </section>

    <section class="host-info">
      <h2>주최</h2>
      <p><strong>PAIS 컨소시엄</strong></p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  :root {
    --primary-color: #1a0f1f;
    --secondary-color: #251730;
    --accent-color: #fd7318;
    --text-color: #ffffff;
    --text-muted: #b8b8b8;
    --color-green: #43d6a8;
    --color-blue: #5fadfe;
  }

  body {
    background: #0d030f !important;
    color: #ffffff !important;
  }

  .workshop-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .hero-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .poster {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .hero-content h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--color-green);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .event-details {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .event-details p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .register-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent-color);
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .register-btn:hover {
    background: #e55f0a;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(253, 115, 24, 0.4);
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  section h2 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .event-info p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .speakers-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .speaker-card {
    background: var(--secondary-color);
    border: 1px solid rgba(67, 214, 168, 0.3);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .speaker-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(67, 214, 168, 0.2);
  }

  .speaker-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-green);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .speaker-name {
    font-weight: bold;
    color: var(--text-color);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .speaker-info {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .robot-preview {
    background: var(--secondary-color);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .robot-preview h3 {
    color: var(--color-green);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .registration {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem;
    background: rgba(37, 23, 48, 0.5);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
  }

  .register-btn-large {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent-color);
    color: white;
    padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .register-btn-large:hover {
    background: #e55f0a;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(253, 115, 24, 0.4);
  }

  .host-info {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .event-details p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .speakers-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>